<h1 class="hero-h">Fractional CMO Nashville: <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">senior marketing leadership for B2B operators here.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">Treetop works with B2B mid-market companies in Nashville and across Tennessee. If you're a founder or CEO between $3M and $30M ARR considering a fractional CMO, here's the Nashville-specific context and how to think about the engagement.</p>
<div class="tldr"><div class="tldr-l">Short answer</div><p class="tldr-p">Treetop offers fractional CMO services in Nashville, TN. Engagements run $8K-$25K/month for B2B mid-market companies needing senior marketing leadership without a full-time hire. Remote-first with quarterly in-person on-site for Nashville clients when scope warrants.</p></div>
</div></div>

<div style="background:#0A1A0A;border-top:1px solid #1A3A1A;border-bottom:1px solid #1A3A1A;padding:1.25rem 2.5rem;">
